@page "/solutions"
<PageTitle>Solutions | Pensoft Systems</PageTitle>

<div class="bg-[#0f1c35] text-white py-16 px-6 sm:px-10 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, #f97316 1%, transparent 30%);"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <p class="text-orange-500 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-2 text-sm">Industries We Serve</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Our Solutions</h1>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen py-16 lg:py-24 px-6 sm:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                We deliver simple and reliable solutions to everyday problems facing many businesses. We are committed to developing and adapting these solutions to fit the ever-changing business landscape across multiple sectors.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Banking</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    We provide different solutions in core banking, system integration, Robotic Process Automation (RPA), and Microsoft Power Apps.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Insurance</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    Applied technology automates the exchange of information and data throughout the insurance lifecycle.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Healthcare</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    We offer a variety of scalable products that provide the features and functionality necessary to meet the needs of any size healthcare organization.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Education</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    In the quest of improving the education system, we offer scalable products that provide the features and functionality necessary to meet the needs of any size learning institution.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Travel & Hospitality</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    We deliver self-service technologies and incorporate customer insights into core business decisions and operations as travel systems move from software to cloud-based ERP.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Public Sector</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    Pensoft is a professional software and consulting firm that provides web-based information software to the public sector.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Retail</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    With emphasis on performance and functionality, Ipen Retail fully supports customer-facing omnichannel and empowers the Enterprise Retailer.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Robotics</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    Technological developments have changed the operations of the global market, and we try to keep up with these trends on Robotic Process Automation (RPA).
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-orange-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Real Estate Sector</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    Development of large-scale and small-scale real estate infrastructure meets unique multi-dimensional challenges to compete in today's global economy.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>